227
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:04,490
-Let's go to the shoot first.
-What shoot?

228
00:17:05,157 --> 00:17:07,760
-Why would I go there?
-Because you're me now!

229
00:17:08,394 --> 00:17:09,862
